 que cumple servicio comunitario ayuda a un inspector destrozado por una infidelidad. Juntos afrontarán el peligro y descubrirán segundas oportunidades."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/mx/title/81937233","overview":"Un psicoanalista tiene que cumplir servicio comunitario y debe apoyar a un inspector devastado por la infidelidad. Juntos enfrentarán peligros y encontrarán segundas oportunidades."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Thérapie de choc","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/fr/title/81937233","overview":"Un psychologue condamné à des travaux d'intérêt général aide un policier torturé par une infidélité. Ensemble, ils affrontent le danger et s'offrent une seconde chance."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Thời khắc quả cảm","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/vn/title/81937233","overview":"Một nhà phân tích tâm lý đang lao động công ích giúp đỡ một đặc vụ đang suy sụp vì vợ ngoại tình. Cùng nhau, họ sẽ đối mặt với hiểm nguy và khám phá cơ hội thứ hai."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Bohaterowie potrzebni od zaraz","runtime":107,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/pl/title/81937233","overview":"Psycholog na zasądzonych pracach społecznych pomaga policjantowi rozbitemu zdradą żony. Razem stawiają czoła niebezpieczeństwom i szukają drugich szans."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Die Stunde der Mutigen","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/de/title/81937233","overview":"Ein Psychoanalytiker im Gemeindedienst hilft einem von Untreue gezeichneten Kriminalbeamten. Gemeinsam stellen sie sich Gefahren und entdecken zweite Chancen."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"שעת הגיבורים","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/il/title/81937233","overview":"פסיכולוג שצריך לבצע עבודות שירות עוזר לסוכן שבגידתה של אשתו שברה את רוחו, ויחד הם עומדים בפני סכנות ומגלים את כוחה של הזדמנות שנייה."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"勇者时刻","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"接受社区服务处罚的精神分析师帮助因不忠而心碎的调查员。他们将一同面对危险，并发现重新来过的机会。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Eroi cercasi","runtime":107,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/it/title/81937233","overview":"Uno psicanalista che deve svolgere lavori socialmente utili aiuta un agente distrutto dall'infedeltà. Insieme affrontano il pericolo e scoprono seconde opportunità."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Čas na hrdinství","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/cz/title/81937233","overview":"Psychoanalytik pomáhá v rámci veřejně prospěšných prací agentovi, kterého podvedla manželka. Společně čelí nebezpečí a nacházejí nový smysl života."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"용자들의 시간","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/kr/title/81937233","overview":"사회봉사 명령을 받은 정신분석가가 배우자의 불륜으로 힘들어하는 한 요원의 심리 상담을 돕는다. 이후 두 사람은 함께 위험을 겪으며 인생의 두 번째 기회를 찾게 된다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Cesurluk Zamanı","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/tr/title/81937233","overview":"Kamu hizmeti cezası alan bir psikanalist, eşinin sadakatsizliğiyle yıkılan bir ajana yardım eder. Birlikte tehlikelerle yüzleşirken, ikinci şansların mümkün olduğunu keşfederler."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"وقت للشجاعة","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/sa/title/81937233","overview":"يساعد محلل نفسي، ملزم بتقديم الخدمة المجتمعية، شرطيًا فيدراليًا حطمته الخيانة، حيث سيواجهان المخاطر وسيكتشفان فرصًا جديدة معًا."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"勇者時刻","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hk/title/81937233","overview":"一名被罰社區服務的精神分析師，協助一位因為配偶外遇而心碎的警探。兩人並肩面對危險，同時發掘人生的第二次機會。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"勇者时刻","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/sg-zh/title/81937233","overview":"接受社区服务处罚的精神分析师帮助因不忠而心碎的调查员。他们将一同面对危险，并发现重新来过的机会。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"SG","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"勇者時刻","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/tw/title/81937233","overview":"一名被罰社區服務的精神分析師，協助一位因為配偶外遇而心碎的警探。兩人並肩面對危險，同時發掘人生的第二次機會。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"وقت للشجاعة","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ae/title/81937233","overview":"يساعد محلل نفسي، ملزم بتقديم الخدمة المجتمعية، شرطيًا فيدراليًا حطمته الخيانة، حيث سيواجهان المخاطر وسيكتشفان فرصًا جديدة معًا."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"AE","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/nl/title/81937233","overview":"Een psychoanalist met een taakstraf helpt een agent die is gebroken door ontrouw. Samen storten ze zich in het gevaar en ontdekken ze tweede kansen."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Η Ώρα των Γενναίων","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/gr/title/81937233","overview":"Ένας ψυχαναλυτής που κάνει κοινωνική εργασία βοηθά έναν ντετέκτιβ πληγωμένο από την απιστία. Μαζί θα αντιμετωπίσουν κινδύνους και θα βρουν δεύτερες ευκαιρίες."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Rohkeiden aika","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/fi/title/81937233","overview":"Psykoanalyytikko suorittaa yhdyskuntapalvelurangaistusta hoitamalla petetyksi joutunutta poliisia. Kaksikko kohtaa yhdessä vaaroja ja löytää uusia mahdollisuuksia."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"Thérapie de choc","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ca-fr/title/81937233","overview":"Un psychanalyste qui doit faire des travaux communautaires aide un agent anéanti par une infidélité, et ensemble, ils affrontent des dangers et se voient offrir une seconde chance."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Modets time","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/dk/title/81937233","overview":"En psykoanalytiker i samfundstjeneste hjælper en agent, der er knust af utroskab. Sammen konfronterer de farer og finder nye chancer."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Vrijeme hrabrosti","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hr/title/81937233","overview":"Psihoanalitičar na društveno korisnom radu pomaže agentu shrvanom supruzinom nevjerom. Zajedno će se suočiti s opasnošću i otkriti druge prilike."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"A bátrak órája","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hu/title/81937233","overview":"Egy közösségi munkát végző pszichológus egy hűtlenség miatt maga alatt lévő ügynököt kezel. Együtt vajon sikerül szembenézniük a veszéllyel és élniük a második esélyekkel?"},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"A Time for Bravery","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/id/title/81937233","overview":"Seorang psikoanalis yang dihukum kerja sosial membantu agen yang hancur akibat perselingkuhan. Bersama, mereka menghadapi bahaya dan menemukan kesempatan kedua."},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"साहस की घड़ी","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/in-hi/title/81937233","overview":"कम्यूनिटी सर्विस कर रहा एक साइकोऐनालिस्ट, बेवफ़ाई के कारण बिखर चुके एक एजेंट की मदद करता है. वे साथ मिलकर खतरों का सामना करते हैं और उन्हें फिर से खुशी के मौके मिलते हैं."},"name":"हिन्दी","iso_639_1":"hi","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Hindi"},{"data":{"title":"A Time for Bravery","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/my/title/81937233","overview":"Seorang ahli psikoanalisis yang menjalani khidmat masyarakat membantu ejen yang kecewa kerana dicurangi. Mereka bersama-sama menghadapi bahaya dan mencari peluang kedua."},"name":"Bahasa melayu","iso_639_1":"ms","iso_3166_1":"MY","english_name":"Malay"},{"data":{"title":"ブレイブ・バディーズ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/jp/title/81937233","overview":"社会奉仕活動を命じられた心理学者が担当することになったのは、妻の浮気に落ち込む刑事のサポート。行動を共にし始めたふたりは、危険な事件に挑みながら、立ち直る道を見いだしてゆく。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Время для храбрых","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ru/title/81937233","overview":"Психоаналитик приговорён к общественным работам после дорожно-транспортного происшествия и получает задание оказать терапевтическую поддержку полицейскому, опустошенному изменой жены. Вместе им предстоит столкнуться с невообразимыми опасностями и обрести второй шанс."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"En tid for tapperhet","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/no/title/81937233","overview":"En psykoanalytiker som gjør samfunnstjeneste hjelper en agent som er knust av utroskap. Sammen konfronterer de farer og oppdager nye sjanser."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"A Time for Bravery","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ph/title/81937233","overview":"Tinulungan ng isang psychoanalyst na nagko-community service ang isang agent na winasak ng pagtataksil. Magkasama nilang haharapin ang panganib at mga second chance."},"name":"","iso_639_1":"tl","iso_3166_1":"PH","english_name":"Tagalog"},{"data":{"title":"A Hora dos Valentes","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/pt/title/81937233","overview":"Um psicólogo a cumprir serviço comunitário ajuda um agente da polícia destroçado pela traição. Juntos, enfrentam o perigo e encontram uma segunda oportunidade."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Vremea curajului","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ro/title/81937233","overview":"Un psihanalist care prestează servicii în folosul comunității ajută un agent distrus de infidelitate. Împreună, ei vor înfrunta pericole și vor începe o nouă viață."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"En tid för tapperhet","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/se/title/81937233","overview":"En psykoanalytiker döms till samhällstjänst och måste hjälpa en polis som drabbats av en personlig kris, och tillsammans dras de in i ett mystiskt mordfall."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Час хоробрих","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ua/title/81937233","overview":"Психоаналітик, якого відправили на громадські роботи, допомагає поліцейському пережити зраду дружини. Разом вони протистоятимуть загрозам і шу